						<summary>

						<p>This record is engraved in vaṭṭeḻuttu script. It registers the gift of sheep for burning a lamp to the temple of Pōrmugasiṅga īśvarattu Dēvar by Araiyaṉ Uttamasīlaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Teṉṉavaṉ Śōḻavaraiyaṉ for the merit of three persons who belonged to Nēchchuṟa nāḍu.</p>						

